# ─── Frontend (Vite) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# No VITE_ env vars are required for production — all API calls go to /api
# which is served by the backend container.
# For local dev with a backend running at a different port, set:
# VITE_API_BASE=http://localhost:3000  (optional — Vite proxy handles /api by default)
